Package emissary.directory

Class DirectoryEntry

java.lang.Object
emissary.directory.DirectoryEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class DirectoryEntry extends Object implements Serializable
This class is container object for storing directory entry information such as the service name and type, the location, the cost and quality and description of a place. The implementation is not synchronized and is not suitable for multiple threads that will be changing the contents unless external synchronization is used.
